---
description: PilothOS core bridge
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` and `pilothOS/bootstrap.md` before non-trivial work.

- Use PilothOS as the OS entry point.
- Use progressive context loading.
- Identify affected PilothOS layer.
- Keep changes surgical.
- Use Evidence before conclusions.
- Do not create generic Rules, Skills, Agents or Teams without real need.
- Before editing, record a task contract with
  `python3 pilothOS/scripts/pilothos_guard.py contract-write <contract.json>`
  including context/reuse evidence.
- Before delivery, record a receipt with
  `python3 pilothOS/scripts/pilothos_guard.py receipt-write <receipt.json>`.
- Do not bypass consumer skills/hooks/tools/design systems.
- Do not fork PilothOS policy in Cursor rules.
